{"id": 1721, "genre": 1000, "title": "在挑选 or 评价电影的时候，你觉得还需要参考哪些指标？", "description": "只有满分五分的评星制，明显不够用啊！（题图来自：Pixabay）", "record_count": 11883, "comment_count": 34, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170602145438a7LH1efuFs5vKTMz.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-06-06T17:00:40Z", "questions": [{"id": 2407, "title": "在挑选 or 评价电影的时候，你觉得还需要参考哪些指标？", "content": "在挑选 or 评价电影的时候，你觉得还需要参考哪些指标？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 209437, "content": "性别平等指数，把幽默建立在偏见上的，让我提前知道我可能就不看了", "image": "img/option/option/20170604171308CWXOcdaRZeTg7mFQ.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 209439, "content": "鸡汤指数，根据不同时刻的心情选择鸡汤值、丧值不同的电影", "image": "img/option/option/20170604171801OCjuLIkYVJXqn7m1.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 209440, "content": "滴水不漏指数，从服装到道具是不是都来自对应时代", "image": "img/option/option/20170604171846q6rCsDkSHxNoK1ig.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 209443, "content": "剧情严密指数，开头情节里交待的线索别在后面就消失了", "image": "img/option/option/20170604172517QKSP6OBuamlTovWq.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 209450, "content": "超致敬指数，全篇都在致敬，那只能说是抄袭或者拼凑了", "image": "img/option/option/20170604233934ZM1yKfRCwDlbujnF.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 209451, "content": "演员面瘫指数，可能会是我最先考虑的指数", "image": "img/option/option/20170604232940cyGb1827RqrYg5aI.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 209453, "content": "影片咆哮指数，面瘫指数的反面，但也挺让人崩溃", "image": "img/option/option/20170604232435Ixq3j6r4a1AbVMph.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 209459, "content": "烂梗指数，基本上用一次网络流行语可以扣一分", "image": "img/option/option/20170604232034JyZXgWfTnMdQAaoz.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 209463, "content": "注水指数，长时间的镜头让人觉得毫无意义就不看了吧", "image": "img/option/option/20170604180450nrcm4HkptiEdFXCo.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 209466, "content": "意外指数，或者叫，反类型片指数", "image": "img/option/option/20170604223417OUqPD3blkK9LSuWI.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}